# Files NOT uploaded to Cloud Build (`gcloud builds submit`). Without this file gcloud derives its
# ignores from .gitignore — which would exclude apps/api/allowlist.json and brick prod (the API
# fails closed when the allowlist is missing). This mirrors .gitignore EXCEPT it intentionally ships
# apps/api/allowlist.json. Secrets (.env*) stay excluded.
.git
.gitignore
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo
.DS_Store
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
coverage/
.vite/
.firebase/
